Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Carter boosted by summit
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040btb9
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 1 Oct 1978
President Carter's popularity boosted by Egypt-Israel summit. Energy plans get more backing. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less